                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10231&quot; title=&quot;sanity-sec test_27: mgs and default fileset mismatch&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10231&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10231&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is closed as dup of  &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10290&quot; title=&quot;sanity-sec test_27: fileset info still not cleared on nodemap&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10290&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10290&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which is landed :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;commit 0dd5215a9e03aae0e01b93e1bd45ab6657af02a9
Author:     Sebastien Buisson &amp;lt;sbuisson@ddn.com&amp;gt;
AuthorDate: Tue Nov 28 10:25:31 2017 +0100
