CommitDate: Thu Jan 25 04:47:29 2018 +0000
    LU-10290 tests: properly set fileset with combined MGT/MDT
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but we still see the issue on several sanity-sec tests (16-25, 27):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;== sanity-sec test 16: test nodemap all_off fileops ================================================== 16:30:16 (1518885016)
mdt.lustre-MDT0000.identity_upcall=NONE
mdt.lustre-MDT0001.identity_upcall=NONE
..
nodemap.active=0
OTHER - IP: 192.168.112.35

sanity-sec test_16: @@@@@@ FAIL: mgs and active  mismatch, 10 attempts 
..
sanity-sec test_17: @@@@@@ FAIL: mgs and active  mismatch, 10 attempts 
..
sanity-sec test_18: @@@@@@ FAIL: mgs and active  mismatch, 10 attempts
..
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the logs for 21e39775a are attached.&lt;/p&gt;
